item.description:
Hello PP2012 People!

You clearly stated your goals for 2012 to the group. So how is it going?

This group is here to listen and help keep you going. Who needs help, who is doing great, and who is sidetracked? Can you please share progress with us. Be open, honest, and tell us just what's going on with you.

We look forward to seeing your progress. We will discuss any challenges you may have encountered putting your goals into real life practice and we will have time to brain storm ways to help you with your challenges. Please keep an open mind.

 

We have only a few months left in 2012. Let's see how far we can get!

 

Cheers,

Donna
item.how_to_find_us: Walk in the room to the right as you enter from the parking lot.
